On the evening of March 7, the metro was empty, single romantics rushed home with packed bouquets of flowers. Petrovich looked at them with warm sympathy. Bubbles of beer, sprats, sauerkraut, sausage, processed cheese stood in formation in the refrigerator. The comp hosted a couple of seasons of The Simpsons, The Big Bang Theory and The Meeting Place Can't Be Changed. It was possible to lie on the bottom during the period of March 8th.